## Consensus Tracking (Spec 258)

```yaml
consensus_tracking:
  enabled: true                  # log consensus outcomes in session JSON sidecars
  acceptance_rate:               # how often operator accepts recommendations unchanged
    formula: "accepted / (accepted + modified + rejected)"
    window_days: 30
    data_source: "docs/sessions/*.json"
    # Surfaced in /evolve F4 and /now. Never auto-escalates autonomy —
    # level changes always require an explicit /config-change decision.
```

